{"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/Transaction\/tracksVelocity","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"metadata":{"fragments":[{"text":"var","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"tracksVelocity","kind":"identifier"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"Bool","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:Sb"}],"role":"symbol","modules":[{"name":"OpenSwiftUI","relatedModules":["OpenSwiftUICore"]}],"title":"tracksVelocity","roleHeading":"Instance Property","remoteSource":{"fileName":"VelocityTrackingAnimation.swift","url":"https:\/\/github.com\/OpenSwiftUIProject\/OpenSwiftUI\/blob\/main\/Sources\/OpenSwiftUICore\/Animation\/Animation\/VelocityTrackingAnimation.swift#L49"},"externalID":"s:15OpenSwiftUICore11TransactionV14tracksVelocitySbvp","extendedModule":"OpenSwiftUICore","platforms":[{"deprecated":false,"unavailable":false,"name":"iOS","beta":false,"introducedAt":"13.0"},{"deprecated":false,"unavailable":false,"name":"macOS","beta":false,"introducedAt":"10.15"},{"deprecated":false,"unavailable":false,"name":"tvOS","beta":false,"introducedAt":"13.0"},{"deprecated":false,"unavailable":false,"name":"visionOS","beta":false,"introducedAt":"1.0"},{"deprecated":false,"unavailable":false,"name":"watchOS","beta":false,"introducedAt":"6.0"}],"symbolKind":"property"},"kind":"symbol","schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"major":0,"patch":0},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"var"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"tracksVelocity"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:Sb","text":"Bool"},{"kind":"text","text":" { "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"get"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"set"},{"kind":"text","text":" }"}],"languages":["swift"],"platforms":["macOS"]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"discussion","type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"This property can be enabled in an interactive context to track velocity","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"during a user interaction so that when the interaction ends, an","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"animation can use the accumulated velocities to create animations that","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"preserve them. This tracking is mutually exclusive with an animation","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"being used during a view change, since if there is an animation, it is","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"responsible for managing its own velocity.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Gesture onChanged and updating callbacks automatically set this property"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"to true."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"This example shows an interaction which applies changes, tracking","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"velocity until the final change, which applies an animation (which will","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"start with the velocity that was tracked during the previous changes).","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"These changes could come from a server or from an interactive control","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"like a slider.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"codeListing","code":["func receiveChange(change: ChangeInfo) {","    var transaction = Transaction()","    if change.isFinal {","        transaction.animation = .spring","    } else {","        transaction.tracksVelocity = true","    }","    withTransaction(transaction) {","        state.applyChange(change)","    }","}"],"syntax":"swift"}]}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI","doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/Transaction"]]},"sections":[],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/openswiftui\/transaction\/tracksvelocity"]}],"abstract":[{"text":"Whether this transaction will track the velocity of any animatable","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"properties that change.","type":"text"}],"references":{"doc://OpenSwiftUI/documentation/OpenSwiftUI/Transaction/tracksVelocity":{"url":"\/documentation\/openswiftui\/transaction\/tracksvelocity","fragments":[{"text":"var","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"tracksVelocity","kind":"identifier"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"Bool","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:Sb"}],"kind":"symbol","role":"symbol","type":"topic","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Whether this transaction will track the velocity of any animatable"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"properties that change."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/Transaction\/tracksVelocity","title":"tracksVelocity"},"doc://OpenSwiftUI/documentation/OpenSwiftUI/Transaction":{"kind":"symbol","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"Transaction"}],"abstract":[{"text":"The context of the current state-processing update.","type":"text"}],"type":"topic","title":"Transaction","identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/Transaction","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"struct"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"Transaction"}],"url":"\/documentation\/openswiftui\/transaction","role":"symbol"},"doc://OpenSwiftUI/documentation/OpenSwiftUI":{"kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Declare the user interface and behavior for your app on every platform."}],"url":"\/documentation\/openswiftui","type":"topic","title":"OpenSwiftUI","role":"collection"}}}